At the supermarket.
A mother and her son (8 yrs) are at the vegetable section.
Their trolly is full of groceries.
The boy is pointing to a poster ‘My Healthy Plate”.
His mother looks at him in agreement.
Another father and daughter (7 yrs) are at the fish and meat section.
The girl is picking the chicken without using the plastic tongs provided. 
The father shows a sign that says ‘no’ because the girl shouldn’t touch the meat with her bare hands for food hygiene reason.